name: CONTAMINATED VOL. 2- The Chernobyl Exclusion Zone

metadata.name: Ballers
metadata.description:
CONTAMINATED Vol.2 is the 2nd part of the OG Collection CONTAMINATED which was minted on OpenSea in August 2021 and has sold 39 works to date and generated a volume of 10.9 ETH. 

https://opensea.io/collection/contaminated

The project was created over 7 years and 4 visits to the Chernobyl Exclusion Zone.  
It is one of the most comprehensive photographic projects about the zone and aims to show all facets of this unique place.
